						               													<description>Have you ever hoped for a voice-activated armadillo launcher? Or perhaps some invisible jelly bean repellent? And should you get your sister that heat-seeking butterfly cleaner she has always wanted? Well, now you can practice finding that special something for your special someone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Perfect Gift is a family-friendly party game for 2 to 6 imaginative players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, one player is the lucky recipient. They select one card from their hand to represent the theme of the gifts that they wish for. The other players choose two further cards from their own hand to create an anonymous three part description of a gift - perhaps cute 'n cuddly boa constrictor slippers, or an oversized chocolate-coated snapping turtle. The players all discuss and debate the merits of each gift, and then the recipient chooses which one they would most like to receive. Whoever created that gift gets a point, and the next person becomes the recipient. The game ends after a fixed number of rounds and the person with the most points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
